  "body": "Found by @D-Nice, I think there is another issue this is a duplicate of, but couldn't find it:\r\n\r\n```\r\ncontract C {\r\n    function g() returns (bool);\r\n}\r\n\r\ncontract D {\r\n    function() {}\r\n\r\n    function f() returns (bool) {\r\n        // call `g()` on `D` (non existing method), but returns `true`\r\n        // due to the memory not cleared after the fallback function \r\n        return C(this).g();\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n```",
